snippet.title: CRITADEL Launch Trailer (Nintendo Switch, Steam, Epic)
snippet.description:
The endlessly replayable 2D action/platform/shooter Critadel is available now! 
Get it on Nintendo Switch (https://bit.ly/Critadel_Switch), Steam (https://bit.ly/Critadel_Steam) or the Epic Games Store (https://bit.ly/Critadel_Epic)
